Invocation Name: moyca subtraction
des: This Alexa skill will help re-enforce basic subtraction skills by repeating addition problems and verifying they are correct. It will work with all Alexa devices and currently supports displays, although it is not required. All subtraction problems are limited to single digit problems and will be non-negative answers.
